<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038484" n="162v"/>
<opener><lb/>Illustrissimo et Doctissimo Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio
                              <lb/>Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>Nic. B.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Meliori valetudini, qua aliquibus post reditum meum diebus caru<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>eram, restitutus jam in eo eram, ut litteras ad Te darem, qu<subst><del>a</del><add>u</add></subst>m
                              <lb/><date when="1718-10-17">nudius tertius</date> <rs key="B_1718-10-16_991170517053005501" type="letter">epistola Tua</rs> gratissima mihi reddebatur, ex qua
                              <lb/>l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus intellexi, Te <rs key="biblio_WIW87HR7" type="biblio">Dissertationem de Nutritione</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3173435" type="place">Mediolano</rs>
<lb/>missam accepisse. Perlectis <rs type="letter">litteris</rs><note type="internal"><!-- Brief ist nicht erhalten --></note> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Patruelis mei</rs> <!-- ToDo Daniel?-->quas <subst><del> apertas</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1221327275" type="person">Mar<subst><del><gap/></del><add>chio</add></subst>ne Bu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tintrochi</rs> apertas</add></subst> simul cum <rs key="B_1718-10-16_991170517053005501" type="letter">Tuis</rs> misisti, non potui non videre propter <rs type="letter">ea</rs><note type="internal"><!-- Dieser Brief von Francesco Fabris ist nicht erhalten. --></note> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
      <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1343364833">Fabris</rs> sibi scripta fuisse significavit <rs type="person">Patruelis</rs><note type="internal"><!-- ToDo SG: persontag--></note>, maluissem tamen
                              <lb/>ne in alienas incidissent manus, ne et alii<del>s</del> videndi et fortassis sequiora
                        <pb facs="1038485" n="163r"/>
<lb/>suspicandi haberent occasionem. Quando rescribam ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruelem meum</rs><!--ToDo-->
<lb/>significabo ipsi ea omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> jussisti. En remitto hic qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> corri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>genda mihi misisti, cum paucis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me notatis. Haud opus esse mi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>hi videtur, ut<add><del> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></del></add> posthac sequentia transmittas, tum quia perpauca
                              <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me notari poterunt, tum quia ego (et fortassis Tu etiam)
                              <lb/>nollem, ut <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenus</rs>, qui<del> omnia</del> cuncta observat, nescio qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sibi
                              <lb/>imaginandi occasionem sumeret. Nomina aliorum de Lingua La<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tina scriptorum nunc non in memoriam cadunt, et puto eos quos
                              <lb/>jam habes sufficere. <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104265264" type="person">Morgagnus</rs> ad quem <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">Librum</rs> Tuum propter
                              <lb/>Anatomica Te missurum esse dixisti, et qui perquam optime in
                              <lb/>lingu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Latin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> studio versatus est, non dedignabitur ad Tuam
                              <lb/>petitionem<del>,</del> ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fortasse melius dici poterunt, corrigere.
                              <lb/>Interim pro lubitu Tuo facies, mihique imperabis Tibi nunquam
                              <lb/>non obsecuturo. Nuper habui <rs key="B_1718-10-08_991170516886805501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzero</rs> nostro,
                              <lb/>in qua salutem plurimam Tibi ascribit. Valde se inquietum esse dicit de negotio suo, idem de me dicere possum expectans
                              <lb/>impatienter hujus rei exitum. Qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so ut mihi scribas, si quid
                              <lb/>oni vel mali accidat, et <add>ut</add> significes, <unclear>c</unclear>um monstraveris <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> <abbr>D<supplied>.</supplied><hi rend="sup">no</hi></abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930" type="person">Paschalico</rs> ea qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> utilia fore judicavimus. Verbo, dignitatem
                              <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzeri</rs> <add>imo et<del> Tibi</del> nostram, Tibi</add> commendatam habe; et si quid forte apud illos, quos time<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mus, efficere speres, id ne negligas.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Patavii</rs> <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> <date when="1718-10-19"> 19. 8bris. 1718.</date></closer>
</div>
